subSubSection.paragraph:
F e m a l e t e r m i n a l i a (
fig. 39
). Both spermathecae dark brown, trapezoidal, elongated with sharp triangular invagination apically. Internal duct invagination cylindrical, well sclerotized, with narrow collar of spermathecal duct near capsule base. One always larger than other. Capsule of the smallest curved at a 45°angle.
